name: GYM_96  (gym_96.wad, gym_96.txt)
description: This is the third installment to the Gym series. I wanted to keep the "run & gun" action of the first two, but I wanted to change the look. Its shaped like a big wheel, with a Main central room surrounded by a circular corridor that is attached by several stairways. There are also many smaller corridors that contain weapons and health.
